                  ),
                ),
                style: TextStyle(fontSize: chipFontSize),
              ),
            ),
          ],
        ),
        SizedBox(height: isSmallScreen ? 8 : 12),
        Row(
          children: [
            Expanded(
              child: Column(
                crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
                children: [
                  Text('다시 켜질 주기', style: TextStyle(fontSize: labelFontSize, color: Colors.grey.shade600)),
                  Text('현재 $currentCycle', style: TextStyle(fontSize: chipFontSize, color: Colors.grey)),
                ],
              ),
            ),
